     H            Y.
     F** AL#RTA  *******************************************
     F* DELETE 20150609,10,11,12,16                        *
     F*      ITS.        2015.05.18                        *
     F******************************************************
     FAL#PP01 UF  E                    DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   60STIME
     I                                        7  140SDATE
      *
     I           SDS
     I                                     *PROGRAM W#PGM
     I                                      244 253 W#WSID
     I                                      254 263 W#USER
     I                                      264 269 W#JBNO
      *-----------------------------------------------------
      *  MAIN ROUTINE
      *-----------------------------------------------------
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     READ AL#PP011                 90
     C           *IN90     DOWEQ'0'
     C           CASHID    IFEQ '20150609'
     C           CASHID    OREQ '20150610'
     C           CASHID    OREQ '20150611'
     C           CASHID    OREQ '20150612'
     C           CASHID    OREQ '20150616'
     C           CAFIXD    IFEQ 0
     C                     MOVEL'D'       CASKJY
     C                     MOVEL*DATE     CASKHZ
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    CAKOME
     C                     MOVELW#PGM     CAKOME
     C                     UPDATAL#PP011
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     READ AL#PP011                 90
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
